---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Digital Twins | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="AI-enabled digital twins that combine data, models, simulation, and decision intelligence."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Digital Twins
      </p>

      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Understand systems. Explore futures. Test decisions.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        Digital Twins combine data, models, simulations, and AI into living decision environments that help organisations understand current conditions, explore future scenarios, and evaluate decisions before they are implemented.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
      >
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            What is a Digital Twin?
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            More than a dashboard. More than a model.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            A Digital Twin is an interactive representation of a real-world system that combines operational data, analytical models, forecasts, simulations, and AI-assisted interpretation.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unlike traditional dashboards, Digital Twins do not simply report what has happened. They help organisations understand why outcomes occur, what may happen next, and how alternative decisions could influence future outcomes.
          </p>

          <p>
            The result is a decision environment that supports exploration, learning, planning, and action.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          Core capabilities
        </p>

        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Bringing together data, models, and intelligence.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Real-time awareness
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Combine operational data, monitoring systems, and external information into a unified view of current conditions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Scenario testing
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Explore how systems respond to changing assumptions, investments, policies, and external shocks.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Risk intelligence
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Identify vulnerabilities, dependencies, bottlenecks, and emerging risks before they become operational problems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Decision support
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Generate evidence-based insight that helps decision-makers compare options and understand consequences.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          Example applications
        </p>

        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Digital Twins for complex systems.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Energy Systems
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              EnergyAI combines market data, infrastructure information, forecasts, and AI-assisted interpretation to help organisations understand energy markets and future system conditions.
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Wholesale electricity prices</li>
              <li>• Generation adequacy</li>
              <li>• Demand growth</li>
              <li>• Renewable integration</li>
              <li>• Security of supply</li>
              <li>• Investment planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Infrastructure Networks
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Understand how transport, water, energy, and communications systems respond to disruption, investment, growth, and changing demand.
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Network resilience</li>
              <li>• Accessibility</li>
              <li>• Capacity constraints</li>
              <li>• Asset planning</li>
              <li>• Investment pathways</li>
              <li>• Long-term forecasting</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Climate and Adaptation
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Explore how hazards, vulnerability, infrastructure, and communities interact under different climate futures.
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Flood exposure</li>
              <li>• Heat risk</li>
              <li>• Vulnerability assessment</li>
              <li>• Adaptation pathways</li>
              <li>• Community resilience</li>
              <li>• Strategic planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Health Systems
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Combine environmental, demographic, health, and service information to understand future health system pressures.
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Climate-health impacts</li>
              <li>• Hospital demand</li>
              <li>• Accessibility</li>
              <li>• Vulnerable populations</li>
              <li>• Service capacity</li>
              <li>• Adaptation planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Decision intelligence, not just visualisation.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Many Digital Twins focus on visualisation. PrincipalAI focuses on helping organisations make better decisions.
          </p>

          <p>
            We combine AI, forecasting, simulation, economic modelling, geospatial analysis, and decision-support frameworks to create Digital Twins that explain not only what is happening, but why it is happening and what actions may improve outcomes.
          </p>

          <p>
            The result is a practical decision environment that supports planning, investment, resilience, and long-term strategy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Build a digital representation of the systems that matter most.
        </h2>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about Digital Twins for energy, infrastructure, climate, health, and policy decision-making.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
        >
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
